        <abstract> 
<p>CD is delighted and astonished at sale of <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>,</p>  
<p>and pleased with sale of others, except <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>. He fears a new edition of that work may never be required. Would have liked to bring out a thoroughly revised one.</p> 
        </abstract>
